@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Index";
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WealthWaveLLC</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="main.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="py-3 bg-light">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <img src="~/Images/icon.jpg" alt="WealthWaveLLC Logo" width="100">
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <p class="lead mb-0">WealthWaveLLC is a premier financial advisory firm committed to providing the highest level of financial guidance and personalized attention to each client.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <section id="services" class="py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Our Financial Services</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                        <div class="card-body text-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-gavel fa-3x mb-3"></i>
                            <h5 class="card-title mb-3">Litigation</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">This service is provided by experienced litigators who offer effective representation in state and federal courts. Litigators are lawyers who specialize in resolving disputes through legal proceedings. They represent clients in court and use their legal expertise to argue on their behalf. Litigation can be a complex process, so it's important to have an experienced litigator who can guide you through the process and help you achieve the best possible outcome.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                        <div class="card-body text-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-balance-scale fa-3x mb-3"></i>
                            <h5 class="card-title mb-3">Investment Planning</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">This service is provided by experienced financial advisors who offer effective investment planning and portfolio management services. Financial advisors help clients manage their investments and create personalized investment strategies based on their financial goals, risk tolerance, and time horizon. They also monitor the performance of their clients' portfolios and make adjustments as necessary to ensure they are on track to meet their goals.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                        <div class="card-body text-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-file-contract fa-3x mb-3"></i>
                            <h5 class="card-title mb-3">Retirement Planning</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">This service provides comprehensive retirement planning and income distribution strategies to help clients enjoy their golden years. Retirement planning involves creating a personalized plan to help clients achieve their retirement goals, such as how much they need to save, when they can retire, and how they will generate income during retirement. It also includes creating an investment strategy that is appropriate for their risk tolerance and time horizon.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                        <div class="card-body text-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-user-shield fa-3x mb-3"></i>
                            <h5 class="card-title mb-3">Financial Advisory</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">This service is provided by advisors who help clients navigate complex financial regulations and provide tailored investment solutions. Financial advisors help clients with a range of financial issues, including investment planning, retirement planning, tax planning, estate planning, and more. They provide personalized advice based on their clients' unique financial situation and goals..</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-5">About Us</h2>
            <p class="lead mb-5">WealthWave LLC is a premier financial advisory firm with over 50 years of combined experience in providing effective financial solutions to businesses and individuals. Our team of advisors is committed to providing the highest level of financial guidance and personalized attention to each client.</p>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                        <img src="~/Images/ManagingPartner.jpg" alt="Team Member" class="card-img-top">
                        <div class="card-body text-center">
                            <h5 class="card-title mb-3">John Doe</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Managing Partner</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                        <img src="~/Images/SeniorAssociate.jpg" alt="Team Member" class="card-img-top">
                        <div class="card-body text-center">
                            <h5 class="card-title mb-3">Jane Smith</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Senior Advisor</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


    <footer class="py-5 bg-dark text-light">
        <div class="container-fluid d-flex flex-column justify-content-between align-items-center">
            <div class="mb-3">
                <h3>Contact Us</h3>
                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> 123-1234</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> info@wealthwave.co.nz</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> 123 Main Street<br>Auckland, New Zealand 0000</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-auto">
                <p class="mb-0">&copy; WealthWave LLC 2023. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>